message.body: hey, sorry i missed your call/text, i was out on an island all last week and had horrible reception. hope you're doing well and adjusting back to life in the states! :)
I'm adjusting. Slowly. What island did you go to?
topsail beach, nc. my dad's side of the family goes every year.
Cool. Did you have fun? Are you back in south carolina now or do you have more travels planned?
yeah, it was nice. back in sc til thursday and then i'll be headed up to atlanta and then chattanooga.
